snippet.title: HOW TO CATCH GORDOS! - Slime Rancher Update Gameplay
snippet.description:
Let's Play Slime Rancher! The new update has added Gordo Snares and the 7Zee Rewards Club to customise your ranch! The Slime Toys help calm down exciteable slimes and they work better if you match the right toy with the slime. The chroma packs lets you customise your home, vac pac and tech color around the ranch! The 7Zee rewards club gives you more chroma pack options and unlocks the slime toys shop. It also gives you ranch upgrades for the fences, paths and other areas!

➤Let's Play Slime Rancher Ep 1 and Playlist: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLX1cB1BI8l6l5NHJMY4cwnJzYP5dDTUy-

Download Josh's mod map for free and take the challenge:
https://joshftl.itch.io/slimerancherchallengemap

http://www.slimerancher.com/

Slime Rancher Info:

- 1,000 Light Years Away: Love, Guts & Slimes -

Slime Rancher is the tale of Beatrix LeBeau, a plucky, young rancher who sets out for a life a thousand light years away from Earth on the 'Far, Far Range' where she tries her hand at making a living wrangling slimes. With a can-do attitude, plenty of grit, and her trusty vacpack, Beatrix attempts to stake a claim, amass a fortune, and avoid the continual peril that looms from the rolling, jiggling avalanche of slimes around every corner.
